docs\schema-phase2-grain-marketing.md:33:Migration 0029 adds optional `moisture_pct` and `moisture_checked_on` fields to the existing `grain_bins` table. Moisture must be between 0 and 40 percent when present. The date is independent so the application can preserve when a check happened even if a reading later needs correction. No existing row is rewritten, and the current grain-bin RLS continues to protect both columns automatically.
